snippet.textDisplay:
Technically it is an outstanding song, it sounds good, makes you dance, but the original emotions of the song are nowhere to be found... This song was never meant to be a dance number... 
It originally talks about separation between a young elephant and his mother and how all the burden has to be borne by him in her absence... It has a way deeper cultural meaning, which i believe hasn't received enough justification...
